BM&FBovespa, JSL Added to Credit Suisse Brazil Model Portfolio

-- B y   A l e x a n d e r   C u a d r o s
-- 
2011-05-02T12:42:42Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-02/bm-fbovespa-jsl-added-to-credit-suisse-brazil-model-portfolio.html
Exchange operator  BM&FBovespa SA (BVMF3)  was
added to Credit Suisse Group AG’s “model portfolio” of
Brazilian stocks on speculation its derivatives volumes will
increase.  JSL SA, a Brazilian transportation company, was also added,
according to a note to clients dated yesterday from analysts
including Andrew T. Campbell.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Alexander Cuadros in  Sao Paulo  at 
 acuadros@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Papadopoulos in New York at 
 papadopoulous@bloomberg.net  